---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="py-16 bg-theme-light px-4"> {/* Section background to theme light */}
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-theme-on-light mb-12"> {/* Main heading color */}
            Struggling To Stand Out Online?
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            {/* Card 1 */}
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition border border-gray-200 value-card"> {/* Card background to white, subtle border, use value-card for hover */}
                <div class="bg-theme-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"> {/* Icon bg: primary with opacity */}
                    <Icon name="tabler:search" class="text-theme-primary w-8 h-8" /> {/* Icon color: primary */}
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-theme-on-light mb-3">Can't Be Found Online</h3> {/* Card heading color */}
                <p class="text-theme-muted"> {/* Card paragraph color */}
                    Your business doesn't show up when customers search for your services. Potential customers go to your competitors instead.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            {/* Card 2 */}
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition border border-gray-200 value-card">
                <div class="bg-theme-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <Icon name="tabler:devices-pc" class="text-theme-primary w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-theme-on-light mb-3">Outdated Website</h3>
                <p class="text-theme-muted">
                    Your current website doesn't represent your business well or convert visitors into paying customers.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            {/* Card 3 */}
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition border border-gray-200 value-card">
                <div class="bg-theme-primary/10 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                    <Icon name="tabler:clock" class="text-theme-primary w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-theme-on-light mb-3">Wasting Time & Money</h3>
                <p class="text-theme-muted">
                    You've tried digital marketing before but didn't see results. It feels complex and expensive without clear returns.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <a 
            href="/contact" 
            class="btn-theme-primary inline-block px-8 py-4 font-bold transition shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105" /* Use theme button class, adjust padding if needed */
        >
            Let Us Solve These Problems For You
        </a>
    </div>
</section>